    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIVILIZATION_CZECHIA_ADJECTIVE" Language="en_US"><Text>Czech</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_OSTSIEDLUNG_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Ostsiedlung</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_OSTSIEDLUNG_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Non-capital cities founded on Hills start with 2 [ICON_Citizen] Population and receive +1 [ICON_Culture] Culture until unlocking the Nationalism civic. After unlocking Nationalism, these cities receive -5 Loyalty per turn.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_LEADER_OTTOKAR_II_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Ottokar II</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_IRON_AND_GOLDEN_KING_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>The Iron and Golden King</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_IRON_AND_GOLDEN_KING_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+30% [ICON_Production] Production toward Heavy Cavalry units. Mines over Bonus, Luxury, and Strategic resources provide +1 [ICON_Gold] Gold.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_RESOURCE_BEER_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Beer</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_IMPROVEMENT_CZECH_BREWERY_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Brewery</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_IMPROVEMENT_CZECH_BREWERY_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Unique Czech improvement unlocked with Guilds. Must be built on Wheat near Fresh Water. Provides +1 [ICON_Gold] Gold, +1 [ICON_Food] Food, +0.5 Housing, and 1 [ICON_RESOURCE_BEER] Beer, a unique Luxury resource. Receives +1 [ICON_Faith] Faith for each adjacent Holy Site, +1 [ICON_Gold] Gold for each adjacent Commercial Hub or Harbor, and +1 [ICON_Food] Food from every 2 adjacent Farms. Receives +1 [ICON_Food] Food with Mass Production and +2 [ICON_Gold] Gold with Chemistry.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CZECH_BREWERY_HOLY_SITE_FAITH" Language="en_US"><Text>+{1_num} [ICON_Faith] Faith from the adjacent Holy Site.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CZECH_BREWERY_COMMERCIAL_HUB_GOLD" Language="en_US"><Text>+{1_num} [ICON_Gold] Gold from the adjacent Commercial Hub.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CZECH_BREWERY_HARBOR_GOLD" Language="en_US"><Text>+{1_num} [ICON_Gold] Gold from the adjacent Harbor.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CZECH_BREWERY_FARM_FOOD" Language="en_US"><Text>+{1_num} [ICON_Food] Food from every 2 adjacent Farms.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_UNIT_CZECH_HUSSITE_WAR_WAGON_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Hussite War Wagon</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_UNIT_CZECH_HUSSITE_WAR_WAGON_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>Czech unique ranged unit unlocked with the Reformed Church civic. Stronger than the Crossbowman but weaker than the Field Cannon. Gains +10 [ICON_Strength] Combat Strength when defending while fortified, and an additional +3 [ICON_Strength] Combat Strength for each adjacent Hussite War Wagon when defending. Upgrades into the Field Cannon.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_ABILITY_CZECH_HUSSITE_WAR_WAGON_WAGENBURG_NAME" Language="en_US"><Text>Wagenburg</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_ABILITY_CZECH_HUSSITE_WAR_WAGON_WAGENBURG_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+10 [ICON_Strength] Combat Strength when defending while fortified, and +3 [ICON_Strength] Combat Strength for each adjacent Hussite War Wagon when defending.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_ABILITY_CZECH_HUSSITE_WAR_WAGON_DEFENSE_STRENGTH_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+{1_Amount} [ICON_Strength] Combat Strength from fortified Wagenburg.</Text></Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_ABILITY_CZECH_HUSSITE_WAR_WAGON_ADJACENCY_STRENGTH_DESCRIPTION" Language="en_US"><Text>+{1_Amount} [ICON_Strength] Combat Strength from adjacent Hussite War Wagons.</Text></Replace>
